  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate a five-session Human Immunodeficiency Virus/Acquired
      Immune Deficiency Disease (HIV/AIDS) group therapy designed specifically for heterosexual
      men. This therapy is compared to standard HIV/AIDS education, which generally consists of a
      single session of HIV education.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
